<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[خَاتِمَةٌ]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٩٩. وَمَا بِجَمْعِهِ عُنِيتُ قَدْ كَمَلْ … نَظْماً عَلَى جُلِّ الْمُهِمَّاتِ اشْتَمَلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٠٠. أَحْصَى مِنَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْكَافِيَةِ»</span>: <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْخُلَاصَهْ»</span> … كَمَا اقْتَضَى غِنىً بِلَا خَصَاصَهْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٠٠١. فَأَحْمَدُ اللَّهَ مُصَلِّياً عَلَى … مُحَمَّدٍ خَيْرِ نَبِيٍّ أُرْسِلَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١٠٠٢. وَآلِهِ الْغُرِّ الْكِرَامِ الْبَرَرَهْ … وَصَحْبِهِ الْمُنْتَخَبِينَ الْخِيَرَهْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>تم بحمد اللَّه<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>